annotationA: Ribosomal protein L10Aa; Structural constituent of ribosome; RNA binding. It is involved in the biological process described with: phagocytosis; translation; neurogenesis
annotationB: 60S acidic ribosomal protein P0; Ribosomal protein P0 is the functional equivalent of E.coli protein L10; Belongs to the universal ribosomal protein uL10 family
